These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
2 different games are played: canasta, bridge
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, dannemann
There 2 different types of food: tomato, orange
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, pakistani
City: london, paris
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, subway
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person traveling to london is the pakistani##1
5. the person eating orange is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola       |
| Game         | canasta   | bridge     |
| Cigar           | swisher | dannemann   |
| Food   | orange   | tomato  |
| Nationality   | pakistani | indonesian |
| City           | london      | paris     |
| Transport     | subway    | airplane   |

