.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, cabbage
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, teacher
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, black
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, july
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, fonseca
1. the teacher is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the fonseca-smoker##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the person who likes black is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pineapple is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Food      | pineapple    | cabbage |
| Hobby         | drawing        | dancing  |
| Job           | police-officer | teacher  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b            | indie    |
| Color   | mauve     | black   |
| Birthday           | june         | july    |
| Cigar     | dunhill           | fonseca      |

